      <description>&lt;!--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Downlink Frequencies - HANA (A): 436.460 MHz, DURI (B) : 436.788 MHz&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modulation: GMSK&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baud Rate: 9600 bps&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protocols: AX.25 and CSP (CubeSat Space Protocol)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beacons Types: Simple Beacon (106 bytes), Full Beacon (69 bytes)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During standby mode, beacons are transmitted every 10 seconds, and the Full Beacon cycles sequentially from Page #1 to Page #2.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The data strcuture for each beacon type is defined as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
